xyz.fsgik.common.net.udp

Interface FsUdpServer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FsUdpClient

    @ThreadSafe
public interface FsUdpServer
extends FsUdpClient
    UDP server interface. The implementation should use FsUdpPacket to represents datagram packet of UDP. And should support following types of callback handler:
    • one FsUdpServerHandler: to callback for server events;
    • a list of FsUdpPacketHandler: to callback for received packet events;
